            <title>[SOLR-12831] DeleteShardCmd doesn&apos;t remove all its data from Zookeeper</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12831</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After successful completion of &lt;tt&gt;DeleteShardCmd&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;there&apos;s still some data in ZK under &lt;tt&gt;/collections/&amp;lt;collectionName&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt; that should&apos;ve been removed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;leaders/shardX&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;leader_elect/shardX&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;terms/shardX&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
